      "height": 410,
      "content": "Sloupecek zustatek: proklik na detaily financniho uctu uzivatele\n\nIkona \"tuzka\" - editace uzivatele (MEMBERS:MANAGE)\n\nIkona \"stit\" - editace opravneni uzivatele (MEMBERS:PERMISSSIONS). \n\nIkona \"bankovka\" - vklad/strzeni castky z uctu uzivatele (FINANCE:MANAGE)\n\nIkona \"user-x\" - zruseni clenstvi / obnoveni clenstvi (MEMBERS:MANAGE)"
